body.p: This model aims to reproduce the negative effects of overexpressing SOD seen in
Zintel et al. 2010 (PMID 20080171).
It is created as part of the GerontoMitoSys project and based on the Bachelor work of Sebastian Ullrich.
Modifications after the Bachelor by Axel Kowald (Axel.Kowald@hu-berlin.de):
05.06.2011 Added non-enzymatic dismutation reaction for superoxide.
13.04.2011 Moved paraquat inside compartment and made reaction unidirectional.
